OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F408A1784729924
OL,3,CMultiple crews tackling large house
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FFire crews are tackling a large house
OL,7,Ffire in Plymouth.
OL,9,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,10,FService said it received multiple 999
OL,11,Fcalls about the incident on Greenbank
OL,12,FRoad, in Mutley Plain, at around
OL,13,F4:45am.
OL,15,FCrews from Greenbank, Plympton,
OL,16,FCrownhill, Modbury, Plymstock, Totnes,
OL,17,Fand Yelverton are all in attendance.
OL,19,FGreenbank Road has been closed in both
OL,20,Fdirections between Mutley Plain and
OL,21,FAldi.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
