OL,3,CMultiple crews tackling large house
OL,4,Cfire
OL,6,FDevon and Somerset Fire and Rescue
OL,7,FService said: "Crews are currently in
OL,8,Fattendance at a large property fire
OL,9,Fnear Greenbank Road in Plymouth.
OL,11,F"Control received multiple calls for
OL,12,Fthis incident. We currently have a
OL,13,Flarge number of crews on scene from
OL,14,FGreenbank, Plympton, Crownhill,
OL,15,FModbury, Plymstock and Totnes.
OL,17,F"This is a developing incident."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
